                            <p>We envision a Uganda where:</p>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled ms-4">
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Political differences are respected without dividing communities</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Citizens prioritize national preservation above partisan politics</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Peaceful dialogue replaces hate speech and violence</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Youth and first-time voters engage constructively in democratic processes</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>National resources and institutions are protected by all citizens</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Cross-party dialogue fosters understanding and reconciliation</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

